title._content: Apollo 11 Mission Image - View of Earth terminator

description._content: Collection: Johnson Space Center Media Archive Title: Apollo 11 Mission image - View of Earth terminator Description: View of the Earth terminator. Image was taken after the transearth insertion as the Apollo 11 crew traveled back to Earth. Original film magazine was labeled V. Film Type: S0-368 Color taken with a 250mm lens. Source: www.archive.org/details/AS11-44-6693 Identifier: AS11-44-6693 SOURCE: nasaimages.org/luna/servlet/detail/NVA2~84~84~85988~137498 Visit www.nasaimages.org for the most comprehensive compilation of NASA stills, film and video, created in partnership with Internet Archive.
